<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><!--ArborText, Inc., 1988-2002, v.4002--><!DOCTYPE Statute PUBLIC "-//Justice Canada//DTD Statute v2.0.0//EN" "Dtd/Version_2.0.0/Statute/Statute.dtd"><Statute bill-origin="commons" bill-type="govt-public" xml:lang="en" in-force="yes"><Identification><BillNumber>C-411</BillNumber><Parliament><Session>2</Session><Number>37</Number><RegnalYear><Year-s>51-52</Year-s><Monarch>Elizabeth II</Monarch></RegnalYear><Year-s>2003</Year-s></Parliament><LongTitle>An Act to establish Merchant Navy Veterans Day</LongTitle><ShortTitle status="official">Merchant Navy Veterans Day Act</ShortTitle><RunningHead>Merchant Navy Veterans Day</RunningHead><BillHistory><Stages stage="consolidation"><Date><YYYY>2016</YYYY><MM>06</MM><DD>22</DD></Date></Stages><Stages stage="assented-to"><Date><YYYY>2003</YYYY><MM>6</MM><DD>19</DD></Date></Stages></BillHistory><Chapter><ConsolidatedNumber official="no">M-5.8</ConsolidatedNumber><AnnualStatuteId revised-statute="no"><AnnualStatuteNumber>17</AnnualStatuteNumber><YYYY>2003</YYYY></AnnualStatuteId></Chapter></Identification><Introduction><Preamble salutation="no"><Provision format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><MarginalNote>Preamble</MarginalNote><Text>WHEREAS the veterans of the Merchant Navy have served honourably and courageously in the defence of Canada throughout the years;</Text></Provision><Provision format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><Text>AND WHEREAS the House of Commons wishes to set aside a day to acknowledge the contribution of the veterans of the Merchant Navy to ensuring the freedom and democracy enjoyed by Canadians;</Text></Provision></Preamble><Enacts><Provision format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><Text>NOW, THEREFORE, Her Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate and House of Commons of Canada, enacts as follows:</Text></Provision></Enacts></Introduction><Body><Heading level="1"><TitleText>Short Title</TitleText></Heading><Section><MarginalNote>Short title</MarginalNote><Label>1</Label><Text>This Act may be cited as the <XRefExternal reference-type="act">Merchant Navy Veterans Day Act</XRefExternal>.</Text></Section><Heading level="1"><TitleText>Merchant Navy Veterans Day</TitleText></Heading><Section><MarginalNote>Merchant Navy Veterans Day</MarginalNote><Label>2</Label><Text>Throughout Canada, in each and every year, the third day of September shall be known as “Merchant Navy Veterans Day”.</Text></Section></Body></Statute>